high_descs: Turn left to face counter with microwave on it.
Open microwave, remove apple from back of microwave, close door.
Turn left, go to refrigerator.  Turn right to face refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, place apple on second shelf down to the left of the egg, close door.  Wait four seconds.  Open refrigerator, remove apple from the left of the egg, close refrigerator door.
Turn right, proceed until microwave is on left.
Open microwave door, place apple in microwave to the bottom left area of the mug.  Close microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Remove apple from microwave, cool in refrigerator, put back in microwave.

high_descs: Take the apple out of the microwave.
Place the apple in the fridge to the left of the egg. Close the door, wait a moment, then take it out again.
Put the apple back in the microwave, to the left of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in a microwave.

high_descs: turn to your left and face the microwave
open the microwave, remove the red apple
go to the fridge to your left; open the door
place the apple on the shelf next to the egg and shut the door; open the door and remove the apple after several seconds
take the apple back to the microwave; open the door
place the apple in the microwave closest to the mug and shut the door
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in the microwave
